32
0:01:36.566,000 --> 0:01:41,000
But attitude, aging is also attitude and health.

33
0:01:41.718,000 --> 0:01:44,000
But my real mentor in this journey of aging

34
0:01:45.418,000 --> 0:01:46,000
is Olga Murray.

35
0:01:46.959,000 --> 0:01:48,000
This California girl at 60

36
0:01:49.749,000 --> 0:01:52,000
started working in Nepal to save young girls

37
0:01:53.45,000 --> 0:01:55,000
from domestic bondage.

38
0:01:55.509,000 --> 0:01:59,000
At 88, she has saved 12,000 girls,

39
0:01:59.9,000 --> 0:02:01,000
and she has changed the culture in the country.

40
0:02:02.393,000 --> 0:02:02,000
(Applause)

41
0:02:03.383,000 --> 0:02:06,000
Now it is illegal for fathers

42
0:02:06.83,000 --> 0:02:09,000
to sell their daughters into servitude.

43
0:02:09.986,000 --> 0:02:11,000
She has also founded orphanages

44
0:02:12.513,000 --> 0:02:14,000
and nutritional clinics.

45
0:02:14.543,000 --> 0:02:15,000
She is always happy

46
0:02:16.196,000 --> 0:02:19,000
and eternally young.

47
0:02:19.697,000 --> 0:02:23,000
What have I lost in the last decades?

48
0:02:23.725,000 --> 0:02:25,000
People, of course,

49
0:02:25.896,000 --> 0:02:28,000
places, and the boundless energy of my youth,

50
0:02:29.743,000 --> 0:02:3,000
and I'm beginning to lose independence,

51
0:02:31.588,000 --> 0:02:33,000
and that scares me.

52
0:02:33.973,000 --> 0:02:37,000
Ram Dass says that dependency hurts,

53
0:02:38.146,000 --> 0:02:4,000
but if you accept it, there is less suffering.

54
0:02:41.039,000 --> 0:02:43,000
After a very bad stroke,

55
0:02:43.175,000 --> 0:02:46,000
his ageless soul watches the changes

56
0:02:46.527,000 --> 0:02:48,000
in the body with tenderness,

57
0:02:48.788,000 --> 0:02:52,000
and he is grateful to the people who help him.

58
0:02:53.3,000 --> 0:02:56,000
What have I gained?

59
0:02:56.37,000 --> 0:03:,000
Freedom: I don't have to prove anything anymore.

60
0:03:00.431,000 --> 0:03:02,000
I'm not stuck in the idea of who I was,

61
0:03:02.996,000 --> 0:03:03,000
who I want to be,

62
0:03:04.126,000 --> 0:03:07,000
or what other people expect me to be.

63
0:03:07.99,000 --> 0:03:11,000
I don't have to please men anymore,

64
0:03:12.04,000 --> 0:03:14,000
only animals.

65
0:03:14.888,000 --> 0:03:17,000
I keep telling my superego to back off

66
0:03:18.43,000 --> 0:03:2,000
and let me enjoy what I still have.

67
0:03:20.612,000 --> 0:03:22,000
My body may be falling apart,

68
0:03:22.671,000 --> 0:03:25,000
but my brain is not, yet.

69
0:03:26.125,000 --> 0:03:28,000
I love my brain.

70
0:03:28.172,000 --> 0:03:3,000
I feel lighter.

71
0:03:31.13,000 --> 0:03:36,000
I don't carry grudges, ambition, vanity,

72
0:03:36.407,000 --> 0:03:37,000
none of the deadly sins that are not even

73
0:03:38.262,000 --> 0:03:4,000
worth the trouble.

74
0:03:40.456,000 --> 0:03:41,000
It's great to let go.

75
0:03:42.2,000 --> 0:03:44,000
I should have started sooner.

76
0:03:44.29,000 --> 0:03:46,000
And I also feel softer

77
0:03:47.036,000 --> 0:03:51,000
because I'm not scared of being vulnerable.

78
0:03:51.06,000 --> 0:03:54,000
I don't see it as weakness anymore.

79
0:03:54.75,000 --> 0:03:56,000
And I've gained spirituality.

80
0:03:57.274,000 --> 0:03:58,000
I'm aware that before,

81
0:03:59.197,000 --> 0:04:01,000
death was in the neighborhood.

82
0:04:01.493,000 --> 0:04:06,000
Now, it's next door, or in my house.

83
0:04:06.794,000 --> 0:04:08,000
I try to live mindfully

84
0:04:09.263,000 --> 0:04:11,000
and be present in the moment.

85
0:04:11.389,000 --> 0:04:12,000
By the way, the Dalai Lama

86
0:04:13.15,000 --> 0:04:15,000
is someone who has aged beautifully,

87
0:04:15.27,000 --> 0:04:17,000
but who wants to be vegetarian and celibate?

88
0:04:17.677,000 --> 0:04:2,000
(Laughter)

89
0:04:24.676,000 --> 0:04:26,000
Meditation helps.

90
